<p class=3D"note-body">A prior section 116, Pub. L. 94=E2=80=93553, title I=
, =C2=A7101, Oct. 19, 1976, 90 Stat. 2562; Pub. L. 100=E2=80=93568, =C2=A74=
(b)(1), Oct. 31, 1988, 102 Stat. 2857, related to scope of exclusive rights=
 in nondramatic musical works and compulsory licenses for public performanc=
es by means of coin-operated phonorecord players, prior to repeal by Pub. L=
