rights and remedies pertaining to any cause of action arising from undertak=
ings commenced on and after February 15, 2067. Notwithstanding the provisio=
ns of section 303, no sound recording fixed before February 15, 1972, shall=
 be subject to copyright under this title before, on, or after February 15,=
 2067."</p>
