shall be held during a 21-day period following the end of the discovery per=
iod and shall take place outside the presence of the Copyright Royalty Judg=
es."</p>
<p class=3D"note-body">Subsec. (c)(2)(B). Pub. L. 109=E2=80=93303, =C2=A73(=
