TY JUDGES!@!Sec. 805 -->
<!-- field-start:head -->
<h3 class=3D"section-head">=C2=A7805. General rule for voluntarily negotiat=
ed agreements</h3>
<!-- field-end:head -->
<!-- field-start:statute -->
<p class=3D"statutory-body">Any rates or terms under this title that=E2=80=
=94</p>
<p class=3D"statutory-body-1em">(1) are agreed to by participants to a proc=
eeding under section 803(b)(3),</p>
<p class=3D"statutory-body-1em">(2) are adopted by the Copyright Royalty Ju=
dges as part of a determination under this chapter, and</p>
<p class=3D"statutory-body-1em">(3) are in effect for a period shorter than=
 would otherwise apply under a determination pursuant to this chapter,</p>
<br class=3D"Q04">
<p class=3D"statutory-body-block">shall remain in effect for such period of=
 time as would otherwise apply under such determination, except that the Co=
pyright Royalty Judges shall adjust the rates pursuant to the voluntary neg=
otiations to reflect national monetary inflation during the additional peri=
od the rates remain in effect.</p>
<!-- field-end:statute -->
<!-- field-start:sourcecredit -->
<p class=3D"source-credit">(Added Pub. L. 108=E2=80=93419, =C2=A73(a), Nov.=
 30, 2004, 118 Stat. 2360.)</p>
<!-- field-end:sourcecredit -->
