03=E2=80=93198, =C2=A72(e), Dec. 17, 1993, 107 Stat. 2308.</p>
<p class=3D"note-body">Section 805, Pub. L. 94=E2=80=93553, title I, =C2=A7=
101, Oct. 19, 1976, 90 Stat. 2598, related to staff of Copyright Royalty Tr=
ibunal.</p>
<p class=3D"note-body">Section 806, Pub. L. 94=E2=80=93553, title I, =C2=A7=
101, Oct. 19, 1976, 90 Stat. 2598, related to administrative support of Tri=
bunal.</p>
<p class=3D"note-body">Section 807, Pub. L. 94=E2=80=93553, title I, =C2=A7=
101, Oct. 19, 1976, 90 Stat. 2598, related to deduction of costs of proceed=
ings involving distribution of royalty fees.</p>
<p class=3D"note-body">Section 808, Pub. L. 94=E2=80=93553, title I, =C2=A7=
101, Oct. 19, 1976, 90 Stat. 2598, related to reporting requirements of the=
 Tribunal.</p>
<p class=3D"note-body">Section 809, Pub. L. 94=E2=80=93553, title I, =C2=A7=
101, Oct. 19, 1976, 90 Stat. 2598, related to effective date of final deter=
minations of Tribunal.</p>
<p class=3D"note-body">Section 810, Pub. L. 94=E2=80=93553, title I, =C2=A7=
101, Oct. 19, 1976, 90 Stat. 2598, related to judicial review of final deci=
sions of Tribunal.</p>
