ceeding to determine the distribution of royalty payments.", substituted "L=
ibrarian of Congress" for "Tribunal" wherever appearing in second and third=
 sentences, and "the reasonable administrative costs incurred by the Librar=
ian" for "its reasonable administrative costs" in last sentence.</p>
