<!-- field-start:referenceintext-note -->
<h4 class=3D"note-head">References in Text</h4>
<p class=3D"note-body">The date of enactment of this section, referred to i=
n subsecs. (a)(2)(B)(i), (c)(3), (5)(A), (d)(2)=E2=80=93(4)(A), (e)(1), (f)=
(1)(B), (5)(A)(ii), (B)(i), (ii), and (l)(2), is the date of enactment of P=
ub. L. 115=E2=80=93264, which was approved Oct. 11, 2018.</p>
<p class=3D"note-body">The year in which this section is enacted, referred =
to in subsec. (d)(2)(B), is the year in which Pub. L. 115=E2=80=93264 was e=
nacted. Such Act was approved Oct. 11, 2018.</p>
